<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Seleccionar Fuente - Reportar Hecho</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        h1 {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: #2d3748;
            font-weight: 700;
            position: relative;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.15);
        }

        h1::before {
            content: '🎯';
            position: absolute;
            left: 1.5rem;
            background: none;
        }

        .subtitle {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .sources-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            min-height: 200px;
        }

        .source-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            border: 2px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            display: block;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .source-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 4px;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #10b981, #059669);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .source-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
            color: #10b981;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .source-item:hover::before {
            width: 8px;
        }

        .source-item::after {
            content: '📊';
            position: absolute;
            left: 1.5rem;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .source-content {
            margin-left: 3rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .source-id {
            color: #374151;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .source-arrow {
            color: #10b981;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .source-item:hover .source-arrow {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .no-sources {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f59e0b, #d97706);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
        }

        .no-sources::before {
            content: '⚠️';
            display: block;
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .no-sources-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .no-sources-text {
            font-size: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-cancel {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #6b7280, #4b5563);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn-cancel::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .btn-cancel:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-cancel:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .navigation-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        /* Indicador de selección */
        .selection-indicator {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1rem;
            right: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #10b981, #059669);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .source-item:hover .selection-indicator {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* Animaciones de carga */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        h1, .subtitle, .sources-container, .navigation-container {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
        }

        h1 {
            animation-delay: 0.1s;
        }

        .subtitle {
            animation-delay: 0.2s;
        }

        .sources-container {
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
        }

        .navigation-container {
            animation-delay: 0.4s;
        }

        .source-item {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
        }

        .source-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        .source-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
        .source-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
        .source-item:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
        .source-item:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }
            
            .sources-container {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            
            .source-item {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            
            .source-content {
                margin-left: 2.5rem;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }
            
            .source-arrow {
                align-self: flex-end;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="container">

<h1>Seleccionar Fuente para Reportar</h1>

<div class="subtitle">
    Elige la fuente dinámica donde deseas agregar el nuevo hecho. Cada fuente puede tener diferentes configuraciones y propósitos.
</div>

<div class="sources-container">
    {{#if fuentesDinamicas}}
        {{#each fuentesDinamicas}}
            <a href="/hechos/nuevo/form?fuenteId={{id}}" class="source-item">
                <div class="source-content">
                    <div class="source-id">Fuente Dinámica ID: {{id}}</div>
                    <div class="source-arrow">→</div>
                </div>
                <div class="selection-indicator">Seleccionar</div>
            </a>
        {{/each}}
    {{else}}
        <div class="no-sources">
            <div class="no-sources-title">No hay fuentes dinámicas disponibles</div>
            <div class="no-sources-text">
                Actualmente no hay fuentes dinámicas configuradas para reportar hechos.
                <br>Por favor, contacta al administrador del sistema.
            </div>
        </div>
    {{/if}}
</div>

<div class="navigation-container">
    <a href="/" class="btn-cancel">
        ❌ Cancelar
    </a>
</div>

</body>
</html>